<!-- SC_OFF --><div class="md"><p><strong>National Counties Cricket Association Showcase Matches 2022</strong></p> <p>These are 50-over friendlies between the professional First-Class Counties and the National Counties (formerly known as Minor Counties) teams nearby. For the First Class counties, these matches act as warmups for the One Day Cup that begins on Tuesday. For the minor counties, it&#39;s a chance to showcase their talents against full time professionals.</p> <p><a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/live/cricket/62208725">BBC Radio Coverage of some games</a></p> <p>It&#39;s unclear how many of the matches will be streamed, if any, but if streams are available they&#39;ll likely be alongside the Scorecards on the <a href="https://live.nvplay.com/ecb/#c659eebc1-5b6d-4115-a3cb-a065bb0fc0da">ECB&#39;s NVPlay website</a> or you can try searching for the names of both counties on YouTube. Unfortunately I&#39;ll have limited internet for most of the day, so might not be able to edit any links that are found into this post.</p> <p>All of the matches start at 11am BST.</p> <p>Today&#39;s fixtures:</p> <p><strong>Bedfordshire vs Northamptonshire</strong> at Dunstable Town CC - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34868">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Berkshire vs Middlesex</strong> at Falkland CC - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34869">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Buckinghamshire vs Surrey</strong> at High Wycombe - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34870">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Cambridgeshire vs Essex</strong> at Saffron Walden CC - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34871">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Cheshire vs Warickshire</strong> at Chester Boughton Hall - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34872">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Cornwall vs Somerset</strong> at Truro - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34873">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Cumbria vs Lancashire</strong> at Sedburgh School - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34874">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Dorset vs Hampshire</strong> at Wimborne - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34875">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Herefordshire vs Worcestershire</strong> at Eastnor - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34876">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Lincolnshire vs Durham</strong> at Grantham - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34877">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Norfolk vs Nottinghamshire</strong> at Manor Park Norwich - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34878">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Northumberland vs Yorkshire</strong> at South Northumberland - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34879">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Oxfordshire vs Sussex</strong> at Wormsley - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34880">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Shropshire vs Derbyshire</strong> at Shifnal CC - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34881">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Staffordshire vs Leicstershire</strong> at Knypersley CC - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34882">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Suffolk vs Kent</strong> at Woolpit CC - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34883">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Wales National Counties vs Glamorgan</strong> at Sophia Gardens - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34884">Scorecard</a></p> <p><strong>Wiltshire vs Gloucestershire</strong> at Cheltenham College - <a href="https://www.ecb.co.uk/matches/34885">Scorecard</a></p> <p>Two more fixtures, Devon vs Somerset and Hertfordshire vs Middlesex are scheduled for Tuesday.</p> </div><!-- SC_ON --> &#32; submitted by &#32; <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/warp-factor"> /u/warp-factor </a> <br/> <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/Cricket/comments/wcjwlm/match_thread_national_counties_vs_firstclass/">[link]</a></span> &#32; <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/Cricket/comments/wcjwlm/match_thread_national_counties_vs_firstclass/">[comments]</a></span>